---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <section class="page">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>
      I am a frontend-focused software engineer who builds fast, accessible web experiences with clear structure,
      strong visual hierarchy, and production-ready delivery habits.
    </p>
    <p class="meta">Open to frontend and full-stack product engineering roles.</p>

    <section class="section" aria-labelledby="about-skills">
      <h2 id="about-skills">Skills</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Frontend:</strong> Astro, React, TypeScript, semantic HTML, modern CSS.</li>
        <li><strong>Engineering quality:</strong> accessibility checks, reusable components, and clear code reviews.</li>
        <li><strong>Tooling:</strong> npm workflows, static-site delivery, and Git-based collaboration.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="section" aria-labelledby="about-experience">
      <h2 id="about-experience">Experience Highlights</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Shipped portfolio and content-focused web interfaces with mobile-first layout constraints.</li>
        <li>Improved readability and interaction quality through typography, spacing, and focus-state refinements.</li>
        <li>Worked in iterative delivery loops with validation gates for type safety and build stability.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="section" aria-labelledby="about-education">
      <h2 id="about-education">Education & Learning</h2>
      <p>
        Continuous learner focused on modern frontend architecture, inclusive interaction design, and practical
        product development fundamentals.
      </p>
    </section>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
